-- Former Barclays banker Maarten de Jong joins Moelis & Co
-- By Olivia Oran
-- Tue May 20, 2014 02:16PM EDT
-- None



May 20 (Reuters) - Maarten de Jong, a former Barclays <BARC.L> investment banker, will join Moelis & Co <MC.N> in August as a managing director based in New York, the investment bank said on Tuesday.

de Jong focuses on clients in the pharmaceuticals, biotechnology and diagnostics sectors. He most recently was global head of life sciences at Barclays.